# Local Verdaccio (`npm run registry`) publish auth: a DUMMY token — anonymous publish is enabled in
# verdaccio.yaml, but the npm CLI insists on a token to publish. Applies ONLY to localhost:4873
# (real installs still hit npmjs). NOT a secret. Does NOT redirect @conti for the monorepo (workspaces).
//localhost:4873/:_authToken="local-dev"
